(5, 'AUTOCAD 2024 win', '2024', '2.00 gb', 'windows', 'La versión más estable para windows con acad.exe\n', 'El progrma usa crack sustituir acad\nAÑO 2024\n\nAutodesk AutoCAD 2024.1.3 [build U.171.0.0] (2023) PC\n\npicYear/Release Date : 2023\nVersion : 2024.1.3 Build U.171.0.0\nDeveloper : Autodesk\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : English + Russian\nTablet : present\nSystem requirements :\n• OS: Windows 10 (version 1809 or later), 11 (64-bit version);\n• 2.5-2.9 GHz processor (3 GHz or faster recommended)\n• 8 GB RAM (32 GB recommended)\n• 2 GB VRAM, 29 GB/s bandwidth, and DirectX 11 support (8 GB, 106 GB/s, and DirectX 12 recommended)\n• 1920x1080 screen resolution with True Color (up to 3840x2160 recommended for high-resolution and 4K displays)\n• 10 GB of available disk space (SSD recommended)\n• .NET Framework 4.8 or higher\n\nAdditionally for 3D modeling and large data sets\n• At least 16 GB of RAM\n• 6 GB of available disk space (excluding the space required for installation)\n• Workstation-class video adapter with 12 GB of video memory or higher, with a screen resolution of 3840x2160 (4K) or higher, with a True Color color palette, with support for Pixel Shader 3.0 or higher and DirectX\n\nDescription : AutoCAD is the world leader in 2D and 3D design solutions. More visual, 3D modeling allows you to speed up design work and documentation, share models and develop new ideas. Thousands of add-ons are available for AutoCAD, which allows you to meet the needs of a wide range of customers. It\'s time to design in a new way - AutoCAD time.\n\nAutoCAD allows you to solve the most complex design problems. The tools for creating freeform shapes model a wide variety of bodies and surfaces; the time for checking projects is significantly reduced; parametric drawings help keep all the necessary information at hand. Design ideas can be visualized in PDF format, as well as implemented in models obtained by 3D printing. Never before have ideas become reality so quickly.\n', 'https://torre9.com/images/ac.jpg', 'https://ug.link/rafa-nas/filemgr/share-download/?id=561a5f842e6249cab6bb175a6c80df3d', 'arquitectura', 'AUTODESK', '2025-07-17', '102', '2025-07-16 22:08:19', '2026-05-27 13:47:49', NULL, 0, 'AUTODESK', NULL, 'WINDOWS 10', 'ESPAÑOL'),
