(115, 'MINI GRAND vst win torrent', '2020', '1gb', 'windows', 'si', 'Year / Release Date : 10.2020\nVersion : 1.2.7 R2\nDeveloper : AIR Music Technology\nDeveloper\'s website : airmusictech\nFormat : VSTi\nBit depth : 32bit, 64bit\nTablet : cured | R2R\nSystem requirements : Windows 8 (64 bit), Windows 7 (64 bit); Minimum Dual Core 2GHz (Intel Core i5 or i7 Recommended)\nDescription : Mini Grand is an easy-to-use yet powerful virtual piano instrument with seven different acoustic piano sounds that suits a wide range of musical styles and production needs.\nThere\'s an old American joke that goes like this: \"Everyone laughed when I sat down at the piano.\" We\'ll never let that happen to you. The piano, perhaps more than any other single instrument, conveys the full range of musical thoughts and emotions like nothing else. Whether you\'re the next Evgeny Kissin bringing the crowd to life at the conclusion of a stirring rendition of Rachmaninoff\'s Piano Concerto No. 2, or Herbie Hancock bringing the funk vibes to Watermelon Man, or Monte Noble making Rihanna\'s music explode on stage, our mission is to provide you with the creative tools you need to reach heights you never thought possible.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/3v21i8ry', 'music', 'sinte win', '2025-07-29', '435345345', '2025-07-29 08:43:36', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, 'AIR MUSIC TECHNOLOGY', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(116, 'TAPE MELLO arturia win', '2023', '224,7 mb', 'windows', 'si', 'Year/Release Date : 08.2023\nVersion : 1.3.0.4471\nDeveloper : Arturia\nDeveloper\'s website : Arturia\nFormat : VST, VST3, AAX Bit\ndepth : 64bit\nTablet : cured (TCD)\nSystem requirements : Windows 10+\n\nDescription :\nTape MELLO-FI is an easy-to-use plugin that adds ambience and vintage warmth to any sound.\nUse its simple preamp, modulation, and filter/output sections to add lo-fi vibes to your mix.\n', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/0jvaxzzn', 'music', 'fx win', '2025-07-29', '45645645', '2025-07-29 10:34:40', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, 'ARTURIA', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(117, 'SERUM 2 - Xfer - win vst sinte', '2022', '1.23 gb', 'windows', 'si', 'WHY SERUM 2?\nThe original motivation for creating Serum was the desire to create a dream synth that didn\'t exist yet:\na wavetable synth with truly high-quality sound, a\nworkflow-focused visual and creative interface to make creating and modifying sounds fun rather than tedious,\nand the ability to \"dive deep\" when needed - create/import/edit/transform wavetables\nand manipulate them while playing back in real time.\n\nSerum version 2 opens up the sonic palette in a big way, offering the user incredible power,\ncontrol and sonic expressiveness - with multiple oscillator types, flexible effects customization, an arpeggiator\nand clip sequencer - the goal of Serum 2 was to give Serum users the ability to fully realize their sonic\nand musical ideas into form. Did we mention that Serum 2 is a free update for Serum 1 owners?\nLifetime free updates actually mean lifetime free updates.\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nMULTIPLE OSCILLATOR TYPES\n\nWAVE OSCILLATOR\npic', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/ezxy5i99', 'music', 'sinte win', '2025-07-29', '6567567', '2025-07-29 10:40:34', '2026-01-06 11:14:16', NULL, 0, 'Xfer', NULL, NULL, NULL),
