(124, 'ADOBE AUDITION 2025 win', '2025', '725mb', 'windows', 'SI', '**Microsoft® Windows 10 (64-bit) v1909 or later**\nProcessor: Multi-core processor with 64-bit support required;\nRAM: 4 GB RAM required;\nHard Disk Space: 4 GB of available hard disk space for installation, plus additional free space during installation (cannot install on removable flash storage devices) Required;\nMonitor Resolution: 1920×1080 or higher display required;\nOpenGL: OpenGL 2.0 capable system required;\nSound Card: ASIO, WASAPI, or Microsoft WDM/MME protocol compatible sound card required\n\n\n\n**Audition es el mejor programa, muy profesional, principal para  hacer audio corrección, restauración y edición profesional para audio para video y música. **\n\n\nEdit, mix, record and restore audio content.\nAudition is a comprehensive set of audio tools that includes support for multiple audio tracks, waveform display, spectral analysis and allows you to create, mix, edit and restore audio content. This effective solution allows you to speed up video editing and audio content refinement, create high-quality mixes with impeccable sound.\nImprove the quality of your soundtrack.\nCreate professional audio compositions using the Essential Sound panel, even if you are a beginner in the field of audio editing.\n\n', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/6jpa1zo4', 'music', 'daw windows', '2025-08-03', '98098', '2025-08-03 12:11:44', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, 'ADOBE', NULL, NULL, NULL),
