(130, 'Piano NOIRE kontakt  torrent', '2020', '14.78 gb', 'kontakt', 'pianos, teclados', '![](https://torre9.com/storage/wHtTvHl11NT1dLlTE0qZXAyIoiOC2liBZB9p2p6h.png)NATIVE INSTRUMENTS NOIRE PIANO\n\nPublisher : Native Instruments\nWebsite : Native Instruments\nFormat : KONTAKT\nQuality : 24 bit 48 kHz stereo\nDescription : Native Instruments has announced the release of NOIRE, a new Kontakt instrument that captures the signature piano sound of composer and pianist Nils Frahm.\n\nThe instrument – which includes both clean and felt versions of the Yamaha CFX 9 concert grand show – was carefully selected in the rich environment of Saal 3 in Berlin\'s Funkhaus recording complex.\n\nThe result is a unique, intense and memorable instrument with its own atmosphere.\nTwo different sets of samples - clean and felt\n\nVersion 1.2.0 2023-09-14\nThe minimum version required is Kontakt 7.6.\nADDED\nSupport for NKS2 navigation\n', 'https://torre9.com/images/noire.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/4wvj4031', 'kontakt', 'piano kontakt', '2025-08-06', '5645645', '2025-08-06 08:31:52', '2025-10-18 08:55:21', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
