(144, 'IK Multimedia - T-RackS 6 v6.3.0 [R2R] SAL|VST3|AAX [WIN]', '2025', '3.24 gb', 'windows', 'mastering win', 'pic\nT-RackS 6 MAX\npic\nYear/Release Date : 01.08.2025\nVersion : 6.3.0\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s website : IK Multimedia\nFormat : SAL|VST3|AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : Present\nSystem requirements : Win 10+\nHITS – MADE EASY\nT-RackS 6\nis the latest generation of IK’s renowned mixing and mastering software. With innovative new modules,\nimproved capabilities, faster workflow and simpler organization, T-RackS 6 delivers legendary sound quality,\nspeed and ease of use, offering everything musicians, producers and engineers need to create the perfect track.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/n82gizel', 'music', 'fx audio win', '2025-08-08', '3434345435', '2025-08-08 04:43:34', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(145, 'IK Multimedia - MODO BASS 2 v2.0.4 STANDALONE, VSTi, VSTi3, AAX x64', '2025', '248.4 mb', 'windows', 'bass ik multimedia', 'Year/Release Date : 06.2025\nVersion: 2.0.4\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s website : IK Multimedia\nFormat : SAL, VST, VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : present (R2R)\nSystem requirements :\nWindows 10 (64 bit) or newer\n\nDescription :\nMODO BASS 2 is the expanded version of IK\'s industry-first physically modeled virtual bass instrument.\nIt adds 8 new basses, including fretless and upright, a new pattern section with a host of new rhythms, expanded controls, and more ways to immerse yourself in the world of MODO BASS. As producers,\nwe all know how important it is to have a great sounding bass line. Available 24/7, MODO BASS 2.0\ndelivers the realism and sound of a sought-after instrument played by a master musician, but with the ease of use of a virtual instrument.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/nmm77q8d', 'music', 'vst win', '2025-08-08', '345345345', '2025-08-08 04:46:27', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(146, ' IK Multimedia - TONEX MAX 1.9.3 STANDALONE, VST, VST3, AAX x64', '2025', '1.9 gb', 'windows', 'fx win', 'pic\nYear/Release Date : 07/30/2025\nVersion : 1.9.3\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s website : IK Multimedia\nFormat : STANDALONE, VST, VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : cured_TeamCubeadooby\nSystem requirements : Requires Microsoft Visual C++ 2015-2019 Redistributable\nv14.27.29016.0 (x64) or greater.\nDescription : Software suite for working with tone models created using AI Machine Modeling technology\nA standalone application and plugin for creating, playing and sharing tone models\nModel amps, cabinets, combos and pedals (distortions, overdrives, fuzzes, equalizers or boosters) on regular studio equipment in just 5 minutes\nEqualizer, compressor, modulation, delay, reverb and noise gate\nSearch and try thousands of tone models of a wide variety of equipment on ToneNET\nUpload your own tone models to ToneNET and share them with other TONEX users\nThere is a free version of the program, as well as 3 inexpensive variations to expand your collection\nUse tone models for practice, jamming or recording in your favorite DAW, on your mobile device with the TONEX App, as well as for live play on TONEX hardware pedals', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/fdhdjkou', 'music', 'fx audio win', '2025-08-08', '345345345', '2025-08-08 04:49:27', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(147, 'IK Multimedia - MixBox v1.5.2 STANDALONE, VST, VST3, AAX x64', '2025', '367.1 mb', 'windows', 'fx audio mastering', 'Year/Release Date : 06.2025\nVersion: 1.5.2\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s website : IK Multimedia\nFormat : SAL, VST, VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : present (R2R)\nSystem requirements :\nWindows 10 (64 bit) or newer\n\nDescription :\nMixBox combines 70* award-winning mixing and creative effects processors into a single, easy-to-use 500-series-style plug-in.\nCreate, compare, and save your own channel sets or multi-effects chains, and choose from over 600 presets to unleash your creativity.\nWhether you use MixBox in your favorite DAW or on its own, it combines a wide range of effects and a powerful workflow to enhance your mixes.\n\nEach processor, based on IK\'s award-winning T-RackS, AmpliTube and SampleTank plug-ins, delivers impeccable sound -\nfrom powerful digital effects to warm, authentic physical models of classic analog gear.\nAnd for reverb, MixBox offers 4 brand new, greatly improved algorithms for hall, room, plate and inversion.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/gc7ogvno', 'music', 'fx win', '2025-08-08', '43534534534', '2025-08-08 04:52:11', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(148, 'Lurssen Mastering Console v1.2.0 SAL, VST, VST3, AAX x64 fx', '2025', '73 mb', 'windows', 'mastering audio win', 'Year/Release Date : 04.01.25\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s website : IK Multimedia\nFormat : SAL, VST, VST3, AAX.\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : Present [R2R]\nSystem requirements : WIN 7+\nDescription :\nLurssen Mastering Console is a completely new approach to digital audio mastering.\nIt provides a complete emulation of the entire technological chain used by world-\nfamous mastering engineers Gavin Lurssen and Ruben Cohen and their team.\nThis chain includes tube equalizers, solid-state equalizers, limiters, de-essers and solid-state compressors.\nThe modeling of this chain reflects their \"whole chain philosophy\".', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/fcw23lmm', 'music', 'IK Multimedia ', '2025-08-08', '3453453453', '2025-08-08 04:57:29', '2025-10-16 15:39:27', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(149, 'iZotope FXEQ v1.0.0 VST, AAX x64 win ', '2025', '124.7 mb', 'windows', 'audio fx ', 'Electrifica tu sonido con Saturate. Añade un toque vintage con Lo-Fi. Modela la profundidad y el movimiento con Chorus, Flanger, Phaser, Reverb y Delay. Transforma cualquier sonido en algo totalmente nuevo con combinaciones y automatizaciones únicas. Desde bajos potentes hasta baterías crujientes y sintetizadores deslavados, nunca ha sido tan fácil infundir un toque creativo justo donde lo necesitas.\n\niZotope FXEQ Bundle v1-0-0 WiN\n5 potentes efectos creativos\n1 innovador flujo de trabajo de ecualización\nAñade dinamismo, dimensión y textura a tus pistas\nOlvídate de enrutamientos, buses y envíos complejos\nDile hola a un sonido brillante sin complicaciones\nMás de 60 preajustes profesionales\n\n\nEnglish\nIntroducing iZotope FXEQ: The EQ that paints effects. Discover FXEQ, the multi-effect plugin that lets you easily add drive, dimension, and texture to your sound by applying powerful creative effects through an innovative EQ workflow – all without complex routing. Electrify your sound with Saturate. Add vintage vibes with Lo-Fi. Shape depth and movement with Chorus, Flanger, Phaser, Reverb, and Delay. Then warp any sound into something totally new with unique combinations and automations.\n\niZotope FXEQ Bundle v1-0-0 WiN\n5 powerful creative effects\n1 innovative EQ workflow\nAdd drive, dimension, and texture to your tracks\nNo more complex routing, buses, and sends\nSay hello to brilliant sound without the struggle\nOver 60 professional presets\n\n\niZotope FXEQ Bundle v1-0-0 WiN', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/yv9goynw', 'music', 'fx win', '2025-08-08', '43535345', '2025-08-08 05:07:37', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(150, ' Skylum Luminar Neo 1.24.4.14984 (x64) Portable ', '2025', '3.00 gb', 'windows', 'Excelente editor de imagenes con IA para WIndows', 'Year/Release Date : 06.2025\nVersion : 1.24.4.14984\nDeveloper : Skylum\nDeveloper\'s website : Skylum\n\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : Multilingual (Russian is missing)\nTablet : cured\n\nAdvertising : none\n\nSystem requirements :\nOS version: Windows 10 version 1909 or higher (only 64-bit OS)\nProcessor: Intel® Core™ i5 or better, AMD Ryzen™ 5 or better\nRAM: 8 GB or more (16+ GB recommended)\nDisk space: 10 GB free space; SSD for best performance\nDisplay: 1280×768 or higher resolution\nGraphics: Compatible with OpenGL 3.3 or later\n\nDescription :\nLuminar Neo is one of the outstanding and most powerful photo editing tools that offers a complete package of AI-powered tools presented by Skylum. Luminar Neo is an easy-to-use software that can be used by both beginners and professionals to create stunning images and photos.\nLuminar Neo comes with a library of beautiful Photoshop filters that can be applied to your photos in just a few clicks. It also offers a wide range of additional features such as face detection, portrait retouching, slider, portrait bokeh, and background removal.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/k57liap6', 'diseño grafico', 'SKYLUM', '2025-08-08', '3453453', '2025-08-08 11:41:27', '2025-10-19 13:25:33', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(151, ' Luminar Neo 1.19.0 (13323) x64', '2024', '3.30 gb', 'windows', 'Excelente editor y procesador de imagenes muy profesional, excelentes resultados', 'Year/Release Date : April 25th, 2024.\nVersion : Build 1.19.0.13323\nDeveloper : Skylum\nDeveloper\'s Website : https://skylum.com/luminar\n\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : Multilingual\nTablet : not required\nSystem requirements : Windows 10/11\nDescription : Features of Luminar Neo:\n- Control the light in 3D space with RelightAI\n- Remove messy powerlines with AI\n- Replace the sky in one click\n- Unleash your creativity with Layers and AI Masking\n- Lightning-fast creative editing with an all-new image engine\n- Speed up your editing workflow\n- Completely transform your photos with new relighting options\n- Easily remove distracting image blemishes\n\nAdd. information :\nOS version: Windows 11, Windows 10 (64-bit)\nHardware: Windows-based hardware PC with mouse or similar input device\nProcessor: CPU Intel Core i5 or better, AMD Ryzen 5 or better\nMemory: 8 GB RAM or more (16+ GB RAM is recommended)\nDisk space: Hard disk 10 GB free space; SSD for best performance\nDisplay: 1280x768 size or better\nGraphics: Open GL 3.3 or later compatible graphics card', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/ult39tgb', 'diseño grafico', 'Skylum', '2025-08-08', '6465465', '2025-08-08 11:46:12', '2025-10-19 13:26:24', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(152, ' Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 4.1.1.23 [Intel/Apple]', '2025', '361 mb', 'mac', 'premiere, final cut, luminar neo', 'Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4\n\npicRelease year : 2024\nVersion : 4.1.1.23\nDeveloper : Native Instruments\nDeveloper\'s website : https://www.native-instruments.com/\nPlatform : Intel/Apple Silicon Universal\nInterface language : English\nTablet : HCiSO\nSystem requirements : macOS 12 and newer\n\nDescription : Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 is the go-to software for hundreds of thousands of DJs at every level. Go beyond the standard with freedom, flexibility, and powerful creative tools.\n\nNative Instruments Traktor Pro 4 is not just an update, but a completely new development based on the wishes and demands of the DJ community.\n\nPowered by groundbreaking technology and relentless innovation, Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 offers an impressive array of features that allow you to fully unleash your creative potential. From cutting-edge remixing tools like iZotope’s AI-powered stem splitting to optimized effects, flexible beat grids, an innovative pattern player, and the built-in iZotope Ozone Maximizer that prevents clipping and distortion of recordings, every detail has been carefully crafted to give you the ultimate DJ experience.\n\nNative Instruments Traktor Pro 4 is the top choice for DJs around the world, from casual mixers to festival headliners. Boost your performance with next-generation tools, high-quality effects, and seamless hardware integration – all designed to give you complete control over your sound.\n\nTake your DJ performances to new heights with Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4, the leading DJ software trusted by professionals worldwide. Whether you\'re mixing at home or headlining a festival, Traktor Pro 4 delivers cutting-edge tools, high-quality effects, and seamless hardware integration.\n\nEnjoy maximum control with features like four-deck control, flexible beat grids, and Ozone Maximizer. Expand your creativity with studio-grade effects, stem splits, and iconic drum patterns. Compatible with all major DJ gear, Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 ensures your sets are always in sync and sound amazing. Get started today and improve your DJ experience with Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4.\n\nAdd. information :\nchanges https://support.native-instruments.com/hc/en-us/articles/360017233958-What-s-new-...raktor-Pro-4-1-1', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/xa84bw01', 'music', 'NATIVE INSTRUMENTS', '2025-08-08', '34534534', '2025-08-08 11:49:57', '2025-11-24 12:48:56', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'MONTEREY 12+', NULL),
(153, 'Native Instruments - Traktor Pro 4 4.0.2', '2025', '1.25 gb', 'windows', 'audio dj daw', 'Native Instruments - Traktor Pro 4 4.0.2\n\npicYear/Release Date : 2024\nVersion : 4.0.2\nDeveloper : Native Instruments\nDeveloper\'s website : native-instruments.com\n\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : English\nTablet : included\nSystem requirements : Windows 10, 11 (latest service pack), Intel Core i5 or equivalent CPU, 4 GB RAM\nDescription : Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 is the perfect software for hundreds of thousands of DJs of all levels. Go beyond the standard, using freedom, flexibility and powerful tools for creative work.\n\nNative Instruments Traktor Pro 4 is not just an update, but a completely new development based on the wishes and demands of the DJ community.\n\nPowered by groundbreaking technology and relentless innovation, Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 offers an impressive array of features that allow you to fully unleash your creative potential. From cutting-edge remixing tools like iZotope’s AI-powered stem splitting to optimized effects, flexible beat grids, an innovative pattern player, and the built-in iZotope Ozone Maximizer that prevents clipping and distortion of recordings, every detail has been carefully crafted to give you the ultimate DJ experience.\n\nNative Instruments Traktor Pro 4 is the top choice for DJs around the world, from casual mixers to festival headliners. Boost your performance with next-generation tools, high-quality effects, and seamless hardware integration – all designed to give you complete control over your sound.\n\nTake your DJ performances to new heights with Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4, the leading DJ software trusted by professionals worldwide. Whether you\'re mixing at home or headlining a festival, Traktor Pro 4 delivers cutting-edge tools, high-quality effects, and seamless hardware integration.\n\nEnjoy maximum control with features like four-deck control, flexible beat grids, and Ozone Maximizer. Expand your creativity with studio-grade effects, stem splits, and iconic drum patterns. Compatible with all major DJ gear, Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4 ensures your sets are always in sync and sound amazing. Get started today and improve your DJ experience with Native Instruments Traktor Pro 4.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/bcsh1gp4', 'music', 'audio dj daw win', '2025-08-08', '4654654', '2025-08-08 11:52:12', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(154, 'Native Instruments - Traktor Pro 3.5.1 x64', '2023', '1.29 gb', 'windows', 'audio dj daw', 'Native Instruments - Traktor Pro 3.5.1 x64\n\npicYear/Release Date : 09.2021\nVersion : 3.5.1\nDeveloper : Native Instruments\nDeveloper\'s website : Native Instruments\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : English\nTablet : present | R2R\nSystem requirements : Windows 7, Windows 8, or Windows 10 version 1803 or later (64 Bit), Intel Core i5 or equivalent CPU, 4 GB RAM\nDescription : Many years have passed since the release of the first DJ software from Native Instruments in 2000. And now the manufacturer has announced the release of a new version of the Traktor Pro 3 program. Traktor Pro 3 today: increased stability, updated graphical interface, higher sound quality, new time stretching, improved limiter, and much more. The user interface has become more readable and convenient. The color scheme is more contrasting, light gray elements have been removed. A new mixer with eight additional effects and three filters has been developed, for a total of over 40 different effects. A new algorithm for time stretching, Elastique 3, has also appeared. The TraktorScratch option for scratching on vinyl with timecode is now supplied with Traktor Pro 3 and can use any sound card for work.\nTraktor PRO 3 is a virtual DJ studio, endowed with the key features of its physical counterpart. This product was developed by Native Instruments, one of the leaders in the music software market. It supports current audio formats, providing the ability to record, mix, and create remixes. The interface is made in a realistic style and fully corresponds to real equipment. Each user can customize the appearance to suit their needs. You can use two or four disc decks. There are all the necessary controls, equalizers, filters.\nThe program is aimed at DJs, but thanks to its simplicity and convenience, it will help ordinary users realize their creative potential.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/ekdol8fv', 'daw music', 'NATIVE INSTRUMENTS', '2025-08-08', '654987654', '2025-08-08 11:54:25', '2025-10-16 15:56:18', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(155, 'FL STUDIO 2024 CREATIVE de 9 gb torr daw win', '2024', '9.00 gb con librerias', 'windows', 'daw win audio', 'L Studio [REPACK]\n\nYear/Release Date : 2024.10.03\nVersion : 24.1.2 Build 4394\nDeveloper : image-line.com\nDeveloper\'s website : image-line.com/fl-studio/\n\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : English\nTablet : cured\nSystem requirements : Windows {8.1} , 10, 11 or later (64 Bit)\nIntel and AMD CPUs. ARM not supported\nThe more powerful your CPU, the more instruments and effects you can run\n4GB of RAM\n4GB free disk space\nMicrosoft Edge WebView2\nDescription : Music studio for creativity.\n\nAdditional information : This is a custom build, if you need it, download the original distribution: Preference for VST instruments instead of Image-line.\n\npic pic pic pic pic pic pic pic pic', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/7ivpbcqq', 'music', 'audio daw win', '2025-08-08', '345345', '2025-08-08 11:57:37', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(156, 'CUBASE Pro 13 v13.0.20 mac daw', '2024', '820.5', 'mac', 'daw mac audio music', 'Steinberg Cubase Pro 13 v13.0.20 Team VR\nDISTRIBUTION UPDATED\npic\nRelease year : 11/29/2023\nVersion : 13.0.20\nDeveloper : Steinberg\nDeveloper\'s website : https://www.steinberg.net/\nPlatform : Intel\nInterface language : Russian + English\nTablet : Present\nSystem requirements : macOS Big Sur, macOS Monterey, macOS Ventura\n\nDescription : Do you want to start making your own music, take your production to a professional level, or optimize your workflow for tight deadlines? Whatever you need, Cubase will help you unleash your full creative potential. From Hollywood blockbuster composers and Billboard Hot 100 producers to aspiring musicians, the entire music production world trusts the wide range of features, easy-to-use tools, and unrivaled sound of our award-winning music production software.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/f9k51lhu', 'music', 'daw mac', '2025-08-08', 'folder download', '2025-08-08 12:01:15', '2025-12-04 09:30:36', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'windows 10', NULL),
(157, 'Aurora DSP L2 Aura VST,AU compressor fx', '2022', '88.5', 'mac', 'fx audio mac', 'Aurora DSP L2 Aura VST,AU\n\npicYear of release : 2025\nVersion : 1.0.2\nDeveloper : Aurora DSP\nDeveloper\'s website : https://auroradsp.com/plugins/l2-aura\nPlatform : Intel/Apple Silicon Universal\nInterface language : English\nFormat : AU, VST3\nTablet : The program is cured (does not require entering data/enter any data)\nSystem requirements : macOS 10.13 and newer\n\nDescription :\n\nL2 Aura is an emulation of a classic vintage tube compressor that provides smooth, seamless compression for vocals, guitars, keyboards and more.\n\nThe plugin offers dual-mono mode and external sidechain for flexible dynamics control, ideal for music producers and engineers looking for a tight and natural sound in the mix.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/2f26e6oj', 'music', 'fx audio mac', '2025-08-08', '34345345', '2025-08-08 12:03:33', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(158, ' iZotope - Neutron 5 v5.0.0 VST3, AAX x64 {R2R} [10/29/2024]', '2025', '190.5 mb', 'windows', 'fx audio win izotope', 'Year/Release Date : 10/29/24\nDeveloper : iZotope.\nDeveloper\'s website : iZotope\nFormat : VST3, AAX. Bit\ndepth : 64bit\nTablet : cured [R2R]\nSystem requirements : WIN 10+\nDescription\n~ Your new flexible, fully equipped mixing console ~\nMeet Neutron 5 - three brand new plug-ins, a faster and smarter Mix Assistant,\nMid/Side and Transient/Sustain modes and much more. Whether it\'s your first mix or the next big hit,\nNeutron always delivers world-class quality.\nWhat\'s new in Neutron 5?\n✱ New! Clipper module.\n✱ New! Phase module.\n✱ Improved Mix Assistant.\n✱ Improved metering and interface.\n✱ New! Density module.\n✱ 7 other intelligent mixing modules.\n[collapse]\nR2R note\nThe witch said,\n✲ The installation of our release is much smaller than the legal version.\nThe original installer copies 10 duplicate DLL files of 250 MB into each plugin installation.\n✲ The original installer adds the Track-Assistant path to HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE. However, we found\nthat Neutron5 tries to read from HKEY_CURRENT_USER. This causes TrackAssistant to crash.\nOur installer adds the path to both HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE and HKEY_CURRENT_USER to solve this problem.', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/mm3t6et6', 'music', 'fx audio win', '2025-08-08', '434354345', '2025-08-08 12:06:22', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(159, ' iZotope - Catalyst Series Bundle (Aurora, Cascadia, Plasma, Velvet) VST3, AAX x64  fx', '2024', '405.9 mb', 'windows', 'audio fx win', 'Catalyst Series Bundle\n\npic\n\nYear/Release Date : 2025-07-29\nVersion : 2025.07.29\nDeveloper : iZotope\nDeveloper\'s website : iZotope\n\nFormat : VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : cured-R2R\nSystem requirements : Windows 10 (22H2), Windows 11 (23H2)', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/xe5dv5pr', 'music', 'fx win', '2025-08-08', '4545645645', '2025-08-08 12:12:55', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(160, 'Toontrack - Alt-Rock EZX (SOUNDBANK)', '2020', '2.56 gb', 'win-mac', 'ezx, ezdrummer', 'Toontrack - Alt-Rock EZX\npicPublisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : www.toontrack.com/product/alt-rock-ezx/\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nDescription : Library for drum module Superior Drummer v3.1.4 + and EZdrummer v2.1.6 + (Only Team VR version)\n', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/3s74ggp3', 'music', 'ezdrummer libreria', '2025-08-08', '456456456', '2025-08-08 12:18:37', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(161, 'Acoustic Songwriter EZX v1.0.0 ', '2020', '16.68 gb', 'win-mac', 'ezx libreria ezdrummer', 'Publisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Toontrack\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nSystem requirements : Requires approximately 18 GB of free hard disk space.\n4 GB of RAM (8 GB of RAM or more recommended).\nThe library works in EZdrummer 3.0.6 and higher, and in Superior Drummer 3.3.6 and higher.\n\nDescription : The ultimate collection of drum sounds designed specifically for acoustic production requires a large selection of vintage and modern kits that can handle everything from subtle nuances to full-on power. This EZX has seven of them. It also needs a great studio. This one was recorded in Nashville. It also needs the best microphones and gear. With two top-of-the-line 48-channel API consoles, Neve preamps, and a mic selection that includes vintage Neumann U67s, AKG D30s, and Coles, this EZX ticks all the right boxes, too. Finally, and most importantly, it needs a producer. In this case, that someone is Dave O’Donnell, a multi-award-winning engineer/producer/mixer who has worked with the absolute top tier of artists for four decades and counting. Listen to his work with the likes of James Taylor, Sheryl Crow and John Mayer and you\'ll understand why he\'s widely considered one of the best in the industry.\n\nWe could go on and on about how legendary drum tech Artie Smith oversaw the setup, that brushes and sticks were sampled on select kits, that both iconic main rooms in the studio are represented, or that absolute must-haves in terms of percussion instruments were also sampled... Ready to make some songs?', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/s37j82mn', 'music', 'TOONTRACK', '2025-08-08', '456456', '2025-08-08 12:21:55', '2025-10-16 23:17:38', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(162, 'Toontrack - Modern Retro EZX v1.0.1 (SOUNDBANK)', '2020', '7.84 gb', 'win-mac', 'audio ezx ezdrummer libreria', 'Publisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Toontrack\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nSystem requirements : Requires approximately 9 GB of free hard disk space.\n4 GB of RAM (8 GB of RAM or more recommended).\nThe library works in EZdrummer 3.0.6 and higher, and in Superior Drummer 3.3.6 and higher.\n\nDescription : This EZX for EZdrummer 3 and Superior Drummer 3 is a collection of unique kits from the mid-1900s era, each hand-picked to create the best mix for everything from acoustic pop to edgy soul, R&B and any thick sounding beats. It was recorded by engineer and producer Christopher Berg (Depeche Mode, The Knife, Fever Ray) and drummer Christopher Cantillo (Carly Rae Jepsen, Mayer Hawthorne, Dina Ögon) at the famous Svenska Grammofonstudion (SGS) in Gothenburg, Sweden. With its main live room boasting an impressive 10 meter ceiling height, yet still with a very low-key atmosphere and tight enough for any modern beats, yet projecting enough air into the room to retain that natural vintage drum tone.\n\nIn addition to the setups, there are a variety of presets included, from raw and naturally organic mixes to completely contrasting ones, including complex chains of saturation, distortion, compression and more. All this, combined with a basic library of drum grooves, will give you all the tools you need to start creating drum parts in no time.\nCopy the EZX3_ModernRetro folder to the directory where the other EZX libraries are located.\nCopy the 1952@EZX_MODERN_RETRO folder to the Midi directory where the other midi grooves are stored.\n\nINSTALACION: \n\nCopy the EZX3_ModernRetro folder to the directory where the other EZX libraries are located.\nCopy the 1952@EZX_MODERN_RETRO folder to the Midi directory where the other midi grooves are stored.\n\n', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/i4wnyimc', 'music', 'ezx ezdrummer', '2025-08-08', '546456456', '2025-08-08 12:24:42', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(163, 'Toontrack - Fusion EZX (SOUNDBANK) torrent', '2020', '14.41 gb', 'win-mac', 'ezx libreria ezdrummer', 'Fusion EZX\n\npicPublisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Fusion EZX\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nDescription : In the fusion genre, where jazz, rock and funk seamlessly blend with an eclectic mix of other styles, drums have always been and remain the defining heartbeat. This EZX for EZdrummer 3 and Superior Drummer 3 aims to uncover some of the defining milestones in the history of the genre and provide you with the finest collection of hand-picked drums. If you\'re looking for big, resonant kits that can handle the entire dynamic range from subtle to explosive and offer tones that span bright, crisp, earthy and warm, this EZX is for you.\n\nFusion EZX was recorded by engineer Stefano Civetta (Nile Rodgers, Ed Sheeran, Earth, Wind and Fire) and drummer Pete Riley (Guthrie Govan, Keith Emerson, Richie Kotzen) at School Farm, a brand new state-of-the-art studio in Essex, England. With its SSL Duality console, gorgeous mic booth, 24 channels of Neve preamps and, most importantly, a spacious but not overly reverberant live room, it was the perfect choice to capture the vibrant energy of the drums in this EZX. There are four unique kits included in total, each hand-picked, tuned and matched to offer their own niche tone and style to the project. What’s more, one of the kits was recorded with two different drumhead setups, essentially giving you a total of five completely different tonal shades. Plus, with kits that boast seven toms each, extras like side snares, octobers, bells, a gong bass drum, several extra kit pieces, and a wide range of cymbals ranging from 6-inch splashes to 23-inch rides, stacks, and chins, this is an EZX that covers a huge breadth.\n\nIn addition to the kits, there are a variety of ready-to-mix presets, as well as a collection of drum grooves and fills, allowing you to instantly start creating drum parts that perfectly combine Pete\'s precise playing with Stefano\'s impeccable, high-quality engineering.\n\nIn addition to songwriting and music production, this EZX was also designed with electronic drummers in mind, offering customized presets with balanced starting points and optimal settings for using electronic drums.\n\nWith all the features you’d expect from a fusion-labeled EZX, but also adaptable beyond any boundaries the genre has to offer, it’s an extension of limitless experimentation and exploration. Much like the genre itself. Ready to create some songs where the drums do much more than just keep time? Enter the fusion universe.\n\nLarge, resonant and articulate kits, perfect for everything from classical to modern fusion\nFour unique 7-tom kits (one of which was recorded with two different drumhead setups)\nWith extra features such as side snares, octobers, bells and a gong bass drum\nA total of 20 cymbals, 10 bass drums and 14 snares\nToms cover sizes from 8” to 18”\nSamples by drummer Pete Riley (Guthrie Gowan, Keith Emerson, Richie Kotzen)\nEngineered by Stefano Civetta (Nile Rodgers, Ed Sheeran, Earth, Wind and Fire)\nRecorded at School Farm Studios in Essex, England\nIncludes ready-to-mix presets for a wide range of sounds\nOffers bespoke solutions for electronic drummers with custom presets', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/lfvjhj90', 'music', 'ezx ezdrummer', '2025-08-08', '345345345', '2025-08-08 12:31:46', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(164, ' Toontrack - Underground EZX (SOUNDBANK)', '2020', '2.43 gb', 'win-mac', 'ezx libreria ezdrummer', 'Underground EZX\n\npicPublisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : www.toontrack.com/product/underground-ezx/\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nDescription : Capturing the raw essence of what drums sound like when recorded using a minimal vintage-meets-modern setup in a cramped basement studio, this expansion for EZdrummer 3 and Superior Drummer 3 presents perhaps the most unpolished, raw and tangible kits you\'ve ever heard. Inspired by punk, hardcore, metal, indie, psychedelic rock, kraut and all the fringe offshoots of the underground scenes from the early 90s to today, this is an eclectic collection of drums that sounds as far off the beaten path as you can imagine. If you\'re looking for an EZX that\'s loud, decadent, angry, and all-around bubbling with unpretentious, carefree, challenging energy, this one\'s for you.\n\nUnderground EZX was recorded by Refused drummer David Sandström and engineer/producer/mixer Martin “Koni” Ehrenkrona at the famed Studio Cobra, a small, low-ceilinged basement studio in the heart of Stockholm, Sweden. From this dungeon-like space – filled with tape machines, old tube gear, and vintage instruments – Koni churned out productions filled with his signature streak of analog character for bands like Refused and Tribulation, to name a few. With a collection of David’s own drums, studio kits, and those of bands and friends in the Stockholm scene, they ensured that this EZX featured four distinctly unique kits, each bringing their own niche sound and vibe to the project. Expect a wide range of beaten, road-worn and time-tested kit that has all been through everything from the big festival stages and underground club scenes to a multitude of albums of all styles.\n\nIn addition to the kits, there is a selection of ready-to-mix presets for each of the four kits. Designed by Coney, these cover everything from completely bare and raw to distorted, all-encompassing menace and feral. In addition, a basic set of grooves and fills performed by David are included, giving you the foundation of his uncompromising and brutal drumming style to build on.\n\nThis is the EZX where you can almost hear the vintage tube gear radiating, the hissing breath, and every wayward and relentless drum hit moving in a way that makes the kits want to crawl out of the monitors. If you want to write a post-punk track rife with lo-fi DYI feels or any streak of wild, distorted and organic sounding kraut, metal, hardcore or garage rock, this is your new EZX of choice.\n\nWant grain? That\'s the definition.\n\n!!!Attention!!! Torrent re-uploaded, folder with midi added!!!!', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/0x8yjeyu', 'music', 'ezx ezdrummer', '2025-08-08', '3434534', '2025-08-08 12:37:09', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
