(177, 'Toontrack - Metal Mania EZX  - torrent', '2024', '12.89 gb', 'win-mac', 'audio ezdrummer drummer librerias ezx', 'Toontrack - Metal Mania EZX (SOUNDBANK)\nLIBRERIA PARA USAR CON EZDRUMMER 2\n\nMetal Mania EZX\n\npicPublisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : www.toontrack.com/product/metal-mania-ezx/\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nDescription : In this EZX, drummer Dirk Verbeuren (Megadeth) and engineer Chris Rackestro (Megadeth, Deftones, Parkway Drive) team up to bring you the ultimate metal expansion for EZdrummer 3 and Superior Drummer 3. It features three unique kits, a plethora of snares and kicks, and over 30 cymbals - all flawlessly recorded in one of the world\'s most famous hard rock and metal studios: Studio A at One On One in Los Angeles. Massive-sounding, warm and alive, yet dense and aggressive at the same time, this room has all the qualities to move air in a way that feels like it was made for powerful metal drums. This is borne out by the many defining records that have been recorded here, some of which include the likes of Megadeth’s “Rust in Peace,” Metallica’s “…And Justice for All” and “The Black Album,” Dream Theater’s “Awake,” and Testament’s “The Ritual.”\n\nEach of the three included drum kits represents its own niche sound. One covers Dirk’s current touring kit, another his tenure with Soilwork, and the third was hand-picked to offer a completely contrasting tone and atmosphere. Overall, you’ll have a balanced yet eclectic palette of kits, covering everything from loud, aggressive, and punchy to big, low, and warm.\n\nIn addition to the sounds, there are a ton of ready-to-mix presets, as well as a collection of drum grooves and fills, allowing you to instantly start creating drum parts that perfectly combine Dirk\'s patented brand of drum madness with Rakestraw\'s crystal-clear engineering.\n\nWith the aim of creating the EZX archetype to encompass every conceivable facet of heaviness – from the raw onslaught of old school thrash and powerful modern metal to the expressive, fusion-like and progressive – the team has exceeded all expectations. This is an expansion that checks all the boxes for drummer, engineer, room, gear and sound. Simply put, this EZX is nothing short of pure and absolute metal perfection.\n\nSamples by Dirk Verbeuren (Megadeth) and engineering by Chris Rakestraw (Megadeth, Deftones, Parkway Drive)\nRecorded at the famed One On One recording studio in Los Angeles\nThree unique kits, each representing their own niche sound, tone and vibe\nA total of 11 snares, nine pairs of kick drums and 34 cymbals\nIncludes a wide selection of ready-to-mix presets designed by Chris Rakestraw\nComes with a selection of MIDI grooves and fills performed by Dirk Verbeuren\n\n!!!Attention!!! Torrent re-uploaded, folder with midi added!!!!', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/1k1ocgks', 'music', 'drums win audio', '2025-08-14', '345345', '2025-08-14 11:50:23', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(178, 'Toontrack - Heavy Rock EZX - torrent', '2024', '7.84 gb', 'win-mac', 'ezdrummer audio ezx', 'Heavy Rock EZX\n\npicPublisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : www.toontrack.com/product/heavy-rock-ezx/\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nDescription : When it comes to heavy rock, there\'s nothing more fundamental than an unwavering wall of powerful drums rolling like a freight train at the forefront of the mix. If you\'re looking for solid sounds that you can trust to hold the rhythm section down in any mixing situation of the sort you may find yourself in, this is the EZX for you.\n\nRecorded by acclaimed mixer/engineer/producer Jay Ruston (Stone Sour, Anthrax, The Donnas) and sampled by drummer Jeff Friedl (A Perfect Circle, Devo, Filter), this expansion for EZdrummer 3 and Superior Drummer 3 brings together two rock heavyweights and delivers exactly what its name promises: drums specifically designed for heavy rock. In total, it includes four unique kits, one additional recorded kit configuration, and several additional snares - all hand-selected to provide a breadth of tones that range from rich, dark, and booming to ringing, tight, and punchy. Additionally, the kits were recorded in a private, high-end studio in the Los Angeles area that boasts a massive sound yet not overwhelming room, making it the perfect choice for loud rock drums that sound thunderous but aren\'t drowned out by excessive ambience.\n\nIn addition to the sounds, the kit includes a wide selection of ready-to-mix presets designed by Ruston, as well as a basic collection of grooves and fills made by Friedl.\n\nIf you want an EZX that\'s smoking hot with raw, unadulterated hard rock energy - recorded by two of today\'s finest using the finest equipment in a room that simply has hard rock written all over it - this is the EZX for you.\n\nFour unique kits and a few extra snares\nA total of five recorded kit configurations, each representing its own niche sound, tone and vibe\nEngineered by Jay Ruston (Stone Sour, Anthrax, The Donnas)\nSampled by drummer Jeff Friedl (A Perfect Circle, Devo, Filter)\nRecorded in a private, high-end studio in the Los Angeles area\nIncludes a selection of ready-to-mix presets designed by Jay Ruston\nComes with a selection of MIDI grooves and fills made by Jeff Friedl\n\n!!!Attention!! Torrent re-uploaded, added folder with midi!!', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/i25zb73m', 'music', 'ezx ezdrummer', '2025-08-14', '34534534', '2025-08-14 11:54:31', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
