(207, 'ARCHICAD V25 mac 2021', '2021', '2,38 gb', 'mac', 'arquitectura mac', 'ARCHICAD 25 DEL 2021 PARA MAC\nNT\n\n1. Disable the Internet\n\n2. Open the folder you downloaded ->> ArchiCAD 25 v25.0.0 (build 4013) macOS 10.15+\n\n3. Install ARCHICAD-25-INT-3002-1.1.dmg and refuse to reboot\n\n4. Install the ARCHICAD-25-INT-Update-4013-1.1.dmg update\n\n5. Unpack (open) the image K AC 25 B 4013 FR.dmg or \"K AC 25 B 4013 INT\" and follow the instructions inside the image\n\n(These files can be used to patch any language version)', NULL, 'http://www.amazon.com', 'arquitectura', 'arquitectura mac', '2025-10-01', '34353453', '2025-10-01 11:07:42', '2025-10-16 13:58:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(208, 'IMAGENOMIC PORTRAITURE 4 mac', '2025', '60 megas', 'mac', 'fotografia photoshop', 'IMAGENOMIC PORTRAITURE 4 ', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/flx7d6dk', 'diseño grafico', 'IMAGENOMIC', '2025-10-02', '789789444', '2025-10-02 08:08:58', '2025-10-16 22:40:16', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(209, 'THE ORCHESTRA v4 SONUSCORE', '2025', '27.04 gb', 'kontakt', 'strings orchestra kontakt', 'Sonuscore - The Orchestra Complete 4.0.0\n\npicPublisher : Sonuscore\nFormat : Kontakt (7.10.7+)\nQuality : Stereo 48 kHz 24 bit\nDescription : Orchestral library\nThe Orchestra Complete 4 is a full-featured virtual orchestra for modern composers, providing everything you need to quickly create cinematic, emotional, and powerful orchestral music. Whether you prefer to hand-write every part or find inspiration with just a few chords, The Orchestra Complete 4 adapts to your creative style, combining stunning orchestral recordings with cutting-edge technology. This powerful tool, created by composers for composers, opens up new horizons in music writing.\n\nAt the core of the instrument is a revolutionary ensemble engine that transforms simple chords into rich, fully orchestrated arrangements in real time. Simply play, and The Orchestra Complete 4 will bring your orchestral ideas to life. For complete control, each instrument is also accessible individually, with a comprehensive collection of articulations and performance techniques.\n\nThe fourth version of our flagship product expands the capabilities of orchestral composition with new content and functionality, while maintaining the familiar ease of use.\n\nThe library includes over 1,150 ready-made arrangements, capable of inspiring any composer, as well as over 300 individual instruments with various articulations. The library includes 80 symphony orchestra instruments, harp, piano, glockenspiel, harp, celesta, organ, choir, percussion, and many others.\n\nNew to this release is \" Forces of Fury ,\" featuring cinematic ensemble strings and powerful, emotionally charged percussion. The keyswitch system offers up to four different musical ideas for each preset, allowing you to create evolving parts with minimal effort.\n\nThe updated collection contains 150 new presets based on thematic musical phrases, ready for use with new keyswitch variations. All presets were created by professional arrangers.\nAn optimized workflow for composers,\nThe Orchestra Complete 4 focuses on music creation, leaving technology behind. Its intuitive design and user-friendly presets keep your workflow efficient, allowing you to focus on creativity rather than technical complexities.\n\nWhat\'s included:\nThe Orchestra Complete 4 takes cinematic composition to the next level without complicating the workflow. Designed for professional composers working under tight deadlines, the library retains everything they loved about The Orchestra Complete 3 and adds even more realism, flexibility, and creative possibilities without changing the intuitive workflow composers rely on.\n\nEnsemble Engine:\nCreate powerful rhythmic patterns and expressive orchestral arrangements using only simple chords—without formulaic phrases or limitations. At the heart of The Orchestra Complete 4 is the Ensemble Engine , which transforms your chords into complex orchestrations in real time. Dynamic strings, powerful brass, and graceful woodwinds will sound in perfect sync with just a single keystroke.\n\nOver 1,000 presets at your fingertips.\nInspiration is always at your fingertips with The Orchestra Complete 4\'s intuitive preset browser . Instantly find the perfect sound for your composition from this vast collection, conveniently organized by library, instrument, rhythmic pattern, and emotional palette.\n\nCustomizable Interface:\nIn The Orchestra Complete 4, each instrument automatically opens with a custom interface. You can change the interface design in the instrument settings at any time.\nFeatures\n• Innovative ensemble engine\n• Play freely or create stunning orchestral colors with simple chords\n• Complete set of standard articulations for all instruments\n• New presets with key switches for 4 music groups\n• True legato intervals\n• 825 ready-made ensemble presets\n• 424 multi-rack patches\n• Add octave function (8va) for a richer sound\n• MIDI export function\n• Fast loading', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/h4yp7s02', 'kontakt', 'Sonuscore', '2025-10-02', '7890005550', '2025-10-02 08:22:24', '2025-10-16 15:41:46', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(210, 'ARVA CHILDREN CHOIR kontakt', '2025', '7,20 gb', 'kontakt', 'strings orchestra kontakt', 'ARVA Children Choir Publisher : Strezov Sampling Website : www.strezov-sampling.com/products/view/arva.html Format : KONTAKT Quality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo Description : Children\'s choir Being in development for more than 3 years the final chapter of Strezov Sampling\'s Next Generation Choir Series is at hand. Starting with WOTAN, the lowest and probably most powerful men choir ever sampled and FREYJA the first sampled choir to focus on the beauty of the female voice, ÁRVA marks the first ever sampled children choir, which is more than just a bonus to the female and male sections.\npic\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCONTACT 5.0 +\n\nWomen\'s choir: https://rutracker.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=5345270\nMen\'s choir: https://rutracker.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=5345444\n', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/68vsbi3m', 'kontakt', 'strings kontakt', '2025-10-02', 'torrent', '2025-10-02 08:25:54', '2025-10-17 08:17:52', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(211, 'Spitfire Audio SYMPHONY ORCHESTRA', '2025', '319,47 gb', 'kontakt', 'Excelente libreria de sonidos de orquesta muy completa: 319 gb es el tamaño', 'Publisher : Spitfire Audio\nWebsite : Spitfire Audio\nFormat : KONTAKT\nQuality : 24 bit 48 kHz stereo\nDescription : World-class musicians\nRecognised by the world\'s finest composers, the Spitfire Symphony Orchestra features a full complement of symphonic strings, symphonic brass and symphonic woodwinds, including solo instruments, plus harp, piano and all the essential percussion elements needed to complete the orchestra, giving your music a professional sound that sets it apart from the rest.\n\nRequirements: Kontakt FULL v7.5.2 or higher!\n', 'https://torre9.com/images/so34.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/zjgxt02x', 'kontakt', 'Spitfire Audio', '2025-10-02', '4650089080', '2025-10-02 08:28:39', '2025-10-18 08:53:41', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
