(218, 'FL STUDIO PRODUCER PRO  torrent v25.1.5  win', '2025', '1,37 gb', 'windows', 'Excelente DAW y trae un pack de plugins de FL Studio', 'Year/Release Date : September 8, 2025\nVersion : 25.1.5 Build 4976\nDeveloper : Image-Line\nDeveloper\'s Website : Image-Line\n\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : Multilingual (Russian is missing)\nTabletka : cured (Warez_Down)\n\nSystem requirements:\nWindows 10, 11 or later (64 Bit)\nIntel and AMD CPUs. ARM not supported\nThe more powerful your CPU, the more instruments and effects you can run\n4GB of RAM, 4GB free disk space\nMicrosoft Edge WebView2\n\nDescription :\nImage Line is releasing an updated version of its iconic workstation software, which boasts a host of new features and capabilities.\nFL Studio is one of the best music production programs available. It lets you create your own tracks in any style.\nIt features all the essential audio features, including recording, mixing, and mastering, as well as over 100 instruments and effects.', 'https://torre9.com/images/fl.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/h9ryfmc4', 'music', 'Image-Line', '2025-10-08', 'rar', '2025-10-08 19:37:59', '2025-10-17 10:14:27', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(219, 'ENSCAPE 4.5.0 para sketch win', '2025', '668.1 mb', 'windows', 'Instalar con internet apagado', 'ENSCAPE PARA SKETCHUP\n\nChaos Enscape 4.5.0.490\n\npicYear/Release Date : 01.04.2025\nVersion : 4.5.0.490\nDeveloper : chaos\nDeveloper\'s website : enscape3d.com\nBit depth : 64bit\nInterface language : Multilingual (Russian is missing)\nTablet : present\nAdvertising : absent\n\nSystem requirements :\n☑ Windows 10 and above.\n☑ Video card: NVIDIA or AMD with 4 GB of video memory or more.\n☑ RAM: 16 GB or more.\n• Revit (2022, 2023, 2024, 2025)\n• SketchUp (2022, 2023, 2024, 2025)\n• Rhino (7, 8 SR3 of newer)\n• ArchiCAD (26, 27, 28)\n• Vectorworks (2023, 2024, 2025)\n\nDescription :\nEnscape is a powerful 3D rendering software. Designed for architects of all skill levels,\nadvanced engineers, and construction professionals, it can perform walkthroughs and VR visualizations of your projects.\nThis plugin easily integrates with popular design programs such as ArchiCAD , Revit , SketchUp , Rhino , and Vectorworks .\nOne of its key features is real-time rendering, allowing users to instantly see changes to their designs as they are made.', 'https://torre9.com/images/enscape.png', 'https://digistorage.net/zw9x8ebe', 'arquitectura', 'Chaos Group', '2025-10-13', 'carpeta 700 mb', '2025-10-13 17:27:12', '2025-10-24 17:15:59', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(220, 'Session Guitarist: Electric Ruby Deluxe (kontakt)', '2022', '17,02 gb', 'kontakt', 'Excelente guitarra eléctrica para kontakt, IMPORTANTE: Requiere kontakt 8.5', 'Native Instruments - Session Guitarist: Electric Ruby Deluxe\n\npicPublisher : Native Instruments\nFormat : Kontakt (8.5.0+)\nQuality : Mono 48 kHz 16 bit\nDescription : Electric guitar with a semi-hollow body and vintage pickups\nSemi-Acoustic Guitar\n• Immerse yourself in the rich, expressive tone of the legendary semi-acoustic guitar\n• Warm chords, smooth solos – play with inspiration thanks to dedicated rhythm and melody modes\n• Reveal vintage charm and expand your sound palette with new amps and effects in Guitar Rig 7 Pro\nJazz, blues, retro pop, and more—\nthe Electric Ruby Deluxe delivers the warm, natural sound of a semi-acoustic guitar with stunning realism. From the gentle whisper of jazz to vibrant R&B solos, every note resonates with depth and expressiveness. Whether you\'re playing velvety chords, soulful strumming, or emotional passages, the rhythm will drive you, and the melody will sing (grooves that swing and melodies that sing) .\nStunning Realism.\nThanks to meticulous sampling that captures every nuance of the hollow body and vintage pickups, Electric Ruby Deluxe delivers a clear and warm sound rarely found among virtual instruments. Slides, mutes, harmonics, and other techniques create a guitar sound so natural, it almost sounds like it\'s being played live.\nTwo instruments in one\n. Switch between two instruments: a pattern engine with hundreds of grooves in various styles and a melodic instrument for detailed parts. Combine them to create complete arrangements or switch between accompaniment and solo – perfect for seamless songwriting, beatmaking, and music production.\nCreate the perfect setup\n. Whether you want a clear, clean tone or a hard, driven sound, 47 ready-to-use presets will help you find your perfect sound instantly. Customize your setup using two direct signals and a mic input, running them through pedals, virtual amps, and cabinets—like the new Reverb Delight , inspired by the sounds of the mid-\'60s. Add the finishing touches with studio-quality effects: compressors, EQ, reverb, modulation, and delay.\nPlay on Kontrol keyboards . The Session Guitarist\nseriesoffers full integration with Kontrol and NKS keyboards. Take advantage of the intelligent Light Guide illumination —it visualizes key ranges, articulations, and performance techniques (slides, mutes, and more), allowing you to easily switch between styles and techniques while playing.\nCreated in collaboration with Big Wave Audio\nSession Guitarist: Electric Ruby Deluxe was created in collaboration with Big Wave Audio - the award-winning team behind Icon Bass , Prime Bass , Electric Sunburst Deluxe , Electric Vintage , Electric Storm Deluxe , Strummed Acoustic , Picked Acoustic , Session Percussionist , Acoustic Sunburst Deluxe and many other libraries.\nFeatures\n• Instant switching between the pattern engine and the melodic instrument\n• A rich set of articulations, including slides, mutes, natural/artificial harmonics for the most realistic sound\n• Adjust loop length, performance style and other parameters in the pattern editor\n• New amp model - Reverb Delight , as well as effects based on Guitar Rig 7 Pro for a real vintage sound\n• Convenient pattern browser, allowing you to quickly find ideal options by articulations, performance style and time signature', 'https://torre9.com/images/ruby.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/8twdclqd', 'music', 'NATIVE INSTRUMENTS', '2025-10-15', 'torrent', '2025-10-15 10:13:50', '2025-10-18 19:38:22', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(221, 'EZBASS mac y update', '2018', '1.00 gb', 'mac', 'EXcelente vst de bajos, ezbas viene con 2 bajos pero existen otras 5 librerías EZB para este excelente instrumento de Toontrack', 'ezbass 1.0 y upodate 1.2 para mac', 'https://torre9.com/images/ezbass.jpg', 'https://ug.link/rafa-nas/filemgr/share-download/?id=1f4e0f6307b54289891340434a62ec63', 'music', 'Toontrack', '2025-10-16', 'torrent', '2025-10-16 16:05:04', '2026-05-02 09:44:25', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'big sur 11+', 'INGLES'),
(222, 'Microsoft Office 2021 win', '2021', '15 MB', 'windows', 'Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, Project en este pack, para windows', 'MICROSOFT OFFICE 2021 PACK WINDOWS \n\nCON WORD, EXCEL, OUTLOOK, POWER POINT ONENOTE, Y OTROS', 'https://torre9.com/images/office21.jpg', 'https://ug.link/rafa-nas/filemgr/share-download/?id=8b95e914389f4e85a39d9b3ee0b84b6b', 'office-pdf', 'Microsoft', '2025-10-17', '.exe 15 mb', '2025-10-17 07:20:18', '2026-05-15 14:28:00', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'win 10', 'ESPANOL'),
(224, 'Session Guitarist - Electric Sunburst Deluxe 1.2 (kontakt)', '2022', '6.4 gb', 'kontakt', 'Sonido de guitarra eléctrica, loops, riffs, muchos loops adaptables y REALES para kontakt IMPORTANTE: requiere kontakt 8.4', 'Native Instruments - Session Guitarist: Electric Sunburst Deluxe 1.2.0\n\npicPublisher : Native Instruments\nFormat : Kontakt (8.4.0+)\nQuality : Mono 44.1 kHz 16 bit\nDescription : 6-string electric guitar\n...the description is being supplemented...\nElectric guitar with a wide range of possibilities\n• Expanded version of the legendary Electric Sunburst\n• Wide range of techniques: fingerpicking, chords and reverse patterns\n• New effects pedals, including delay, chorus, flanger and phaser\n• Includes an additional tool for composing melodies and creating patterns\nThe Session Electric Player You Requested\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE is a powerful, expanded version of the hugely popular ELECTRIC SUNBURST. This DELUXE instrument draws from the same meticulously captured iconic electric guitar and adds a wealth of user-requested features, including a second instrument for melodic playing, more patterns, enhanced performance controls, and new effects. With a fully versatile instrument, you can produce authentic, finished tracks for any modern production effortlessly.\nTight Rhythms To Custom Melodies\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE gives you two KONTAKT instruments for creating complete, authentic electric guitar parts. The pattern-based instrument lets you instantly generate riffs, strumming patterns, and arpeggios simply by playing a chord on your MIDI controller. The included melody instrument enables you to combine your own, freely playable melodies with the integrated patterns. Smooth transitions between melodies and patterns help you deliver unique, engaging electric guitar parts for any production.\nExpanded Sonic Toolbox\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE features a high-quality collection of effects, amps, and cabinet emulations. The DELUXE instrument adds all-new chorus, flanger, and phaser stomp pedals to the original array of classic distortion and modulation effects. Five amplifier models and a choice of ten cabinets let you dial in your tone. High-quality console EQ, two vintage compressors, tape emulation, reverb, delay, tape delay plus newly added REPLIKA delay and a studio-grade algorithmic reverb allow you to produce complete, finished tracks entirely within the instrument.\nThe Guitar\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE captures an iconic electric guitar chosen for its rich, warm, and highly adaptable sound. A pristine signal path – including high-end cables, vintage tube preamps, and high-resolution converters – ensured that every nuance of this legendary instrument was accurately captured. With separate bridge and neck pickup samples, you can take full control of the mix balance. Blend in fine sonic details from a condenser mic mounted above the strings to add punch and realism to the performance.\nExtensive Patterns\nTap into 237 patterns, including realistic riffs, arpeggios, strummed intervals, and chords. ELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE adds new strumming and arpeggio patterns plus an assortment of reverse patterns to spark new ideas. With patterns grouped into song presets, you can immediately find what you need, whether you’re working on a pop production or electronic tracks.\nEnhanced Performance Controls\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE offers an expanded range of performance controls to give you unmatched flexibility, realism, and tonal variety. Access thousands of loops, single notes, and noises over numerous fret positions – played both with plectrum and fingers in open, muted, flageolet and tremolo articulations. The DELUXE instrument adds real-time bending and vibrato controls – with multiple vibrato speeds – so you can add greater expression to your parts. Innovative pitch bend presets allow the bending of only selected notes of a voicing to emulate typical bending techniques.\n\nAn autochord mode and convenient voicing presets let you program or perform authentic electric guitar parts – even if you’re not a guitarist. Advanced voicing capabilities available with this DELUXE instrument let you explore new arrangement options.\nFinely Tuned Feel\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE features an improved playback and picking engine that lets you fine-tune the feel of your parts. Tuning, timing, and humanization settings help you create live-sounding performances that can work in any genre.\nKomplete Kontrol Integration\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE takes full advantage of KOMPLETE KONTROL hardware and the NKS standard, offering advantages such as hardware browsing and audio previews, light guide display of keyranges and articulations, and more.\nCreated With Drumasonic\nELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE was created in collaboration with drumasonic – the same award-winning sample instrument team behind ELECTRIC SUNBURST and STRUMMED ACOUSTIC instruments.\nВозможности\n• Add the authentic professional sound of a top session player and access a full range of performance controls for your next production.\n• Load the included melodic instrument to play your own melodies and arpeggios, using open, muted, flageolet and tremolo articulations – each available with finger and plectrum.\n• This meticulously recorded electric guitar was chosen for a rich, adaptable sound that can work in a wide variety of contemporary styles and genres.\n• Customize playability and sound using the enhanced Guitar Settings page.\n• Create realistic performances and sculpt your sound with enhanced performance and playback parameters.\n• Deliver a finished track entirely within ELECTRIC SUNBURST DELUXE. Choose from a wide array of pedals, amp and cab combinations, plus studio-grade mixing effects.\n• Find what you need fast with a dynamic pattern search function that lets you locate patterns by time signature, playing style, and more. Or input your desired rhythmic structure manually.', 'https://torre9.com/images/electrics1.png', 'https://digistorage.net/b01j85u6', 'kontakt', 'NATIVE INSTRUMENTS', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 09:28:00', '2025-10-18 19:38:44', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
