(230, 'Session Guitarist: Electric Storm Deluxe kontakt', '2021', '18.25 gb', 'kontakt', '5 octavas, 8 cuerdas, excelente sonido real y loops. Requiere Kontakt 8.1', '**Native Instruments - Session Guitarist: Electric Storm Deluxe**\n\npicPublisher : Native Instruments\nFormat : Kontakt (8.1.0+)\nQuality : Mono 48 kHz 16 bit\nDescription : Eight-string electric guitar\nEight-String Metal Guitar\n• Five-octave-spanning eight-string electric guitar with a drop-style feel and powerful lows\n• Create relentless riffs and jaw-dropping solos with 270 patterns\n• Shape any tone with advanced amp and stompbox emulators powered by Guitar Rig 7 Pro\nDrop-Tuning Destruction.\nFrom piercing leads to crushing riffs, the Electric Storm Deluxe unleashes the full power and range of a premium eight-string electric guitar. Crafted for the furious sounds of metal, rock, industrial, and more, it delivers thunderous lows, soaring solos, and everything in between. Whether you\'re writing for a mosh pit or dramatic movie moments, the Electric Storm Deluxe delivers stunning tone on demand.\n\n\n\nThe power and precision\nof the Electric Storm Deluxe was carefully sampled from the Framus Custom Shop Panthera to preserve its stunning lows and impeccable precision. Equipped with two pickups and an additional mic mounted above the strings, it superbly reproduces high-gain and artificial harmonics with flexible switching between neck, bridge, and middle positions. Its 24 frets offer unrivaled range for expressive solos and complex melodies.\n\nTwo Performance Modes\n: Explore two performance modes: a pattern-based engine for creating instant riffs and a melodic mode for crafting complex solos and leads note-by-note. Seamlessly integrated, these two tools let you switch between fast, heavy riffs and solos, providing everything you need to create impressive guitar parts.\n\nAuthentic Riffs and Melodies:\nBrowse 270 riffs and picking patterns, from fast 16th-note rhythms to complex sweeps, muted strumming, and fast tapping. Get inspired by the included phrases and chord progressions, which support drag-and-drop MIDI files for further editing in your DAW. Adjust swing, humanization, and accents to create a natural feel, while the mechanism provides realistic hammer-ons, pull-offs, slides, tapping, as well as vibrato and tremolo arm options.\n\nCreate your own guitar rig.\nChoose from 54 sound presets in categories like Clean , Crunch , High-gain , Lead , Modulation , and SFX/Scoring , or create your own tones with two DI signals and a mic signal. Route your sound through three parallel chains with virtual amps, cabinets, stompboxes, and studio effects like compressor, EQ, reverb, distortion, modulation, and delay. New amp models, adjustable speaker impulse response, and parallel amp chains open up endless sound design possibilities.\nPlay on Kontrol keyboards . The Session Guitarist\nseriesoffers full integration with NKS and Kontrol keyboards. Take advantage of the Light Guide to display key ranges, articulations, and expressive techniques like slides and mutes, making it easy to switch between playing styles and articulations during a take.\nCreated in collaboration with Drumasonic\nSession Guitarist: Electric Storm Deluxe was created in collaboration with Drumasonic - the award-winning team behind Icon Bass , Prime Bass , Electric Sunburst Deluxe , Electric Vintage , Strummed Acoustic , Picked Acoustic , Session Percussionist , Acoustic Sunburst Deluxe and many other libraries.', 'https://torre9.com/images/esd.png', 'https://digistorage.net/zqeoi8tm', 'music', 'NATIVE INSTRUMENTS', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 10:19:42', '2025-10-18 19:36:08', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(231, 'EBX Funk Fusion para EZBass', '2025', '1.09', 'win-mac', 'Excelente libreria para EZ Bass  Expansion EBX', 'Publisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Toontrack\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\n\nDescription : This EZbass library was created with the goal of creating the perfect instrument to bridge the gap between two genres in which bass has been a rhythmic foundation since its inception: funk and fusion. This bass guitar is a flawlessly crafted modern instrument designed to deliver the highest standards of sound, dynamics, and tonal depth. Because this bass guitar needed to handle the intricacies of jazz and rock equally well, it was chosen from a number of instruments because it perfectly matched all parameters. The sample was recorded using traditional fingerpicking and quintessential slapping techniques, as well as a completely new articulation for EZbass called lefthand mute. The latter will allow you to achieve a coherent and distinct performance, very reminiscent of a mute on an electric guitar and crucial to the sound of these genres.\n\nBeyond the bass itself, this EBX also includes a wide selection of presets, as well as a basic collection of basslines tailored for funk and fusion. The presets cover the entire spectrum from classical to contemporary, and include everything from basic and subdued to spacious, airy, and rich. The presets even feature an FM synth layer, allowing you to seamlessly layer the texture of a classic synth bass over a regular instrument. Furthermore, the MIDI file contains all the necessary components for creating any funk or fusion track.\n\nHuge thanks to the highly respected: JohnBadger !', 'https://torre9.com/images/ebxff.png', 'https://digistorage.net/p5qia8tu', 'music', 'TOONTRACK', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 10:24:56', '2025-10-18 10:57:16', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(232, 'EBX Hollowbody para EZBass', '2018', '985.2', 'win-mac', 'Para músicos amantes del Acoustic Music Pop', 'EBX Hollowbody para EZBass', 'https://torre9.com/images/hb.png', 'https://digistorage.net/z12oqtyy', 'music', 'TOONTRACK', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 10:28:12', '2025-10-18 10:56:58', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(233, 'EBX Synth Bass para EZBass', '2023', '1.63', 'win-mac', 'Basado en sintetizadores Vintage y modernos, Librería para EZBass', 'Publisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Toontrack\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\n\nDescription : Based on some of the most influential vintage and modern synths, but reworked, richly textured, and richly textured, this EZbass expansion presents a collection of bass tones unlike anything you\'ve ever heard. If you\'re looking for a library that combines a minty, organic vintage vibe with cutting-edge sound design, this is your new choice.\n\nSix carefully selected hardware synthesizer instruments served as the foundation for this EBX. The design team then added layers of field recording noise, modular synthesis, granular modular tones, foley, and various other ambiences to create richly textured and layered bass tones. Each sound was then individually processed, enriched, and corrected using vintage hardware compressors, EQs, and external vacuum tubes to add even more organic warmth, grit, and gain. The result? A patchwork of 75 hybrid synth bass sounds, covering the entire spectrum: from dense, bold, clean, and pristine to thunderous drone ambience, dirty, distorted, and aggressive.\n\nIn addition to the sounds, a fundamental collection of MIDI building blocks is included, as well as basic, melodic, and arpeggiated patterns unique to the product.\n\nIf you\'re looking for a wide range of timeless bass sounds based on iconic synths but in completely new outfits, this EBX is for you. Get ready for altered, distorted, twisted, and twisted timbres designed to redefine your basslines, whether pop, electronic, ambient, or anything in between.\n\nHuge thanks to: JohnBadger !', 'https://torre9.com/images/sba.png', 'https://digistorage.net/aw4v9l7c', 'music', 'TOONTRACK', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 10:32:08', '2025-10-18 10:56:49', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(234, 'EBX Acoustic para EZBass', '2023', '1.09 gb', 'win-mac', 'EZB Acoustic para EZBass', 'Toontrack Acoustic EBX\n\n\n[https://torre9.com/images/ebxac34.png](https://)\n\npicPublisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Toontrack\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24-bit 44.1 kHz stereo\nDescription : The Acoustic EBX is an EZbass expansion featuring a traditional four-string acoustic bass guitar. Recorded with both an external condenser microphone and a built-in piezo pickup, it offers the absolute best of both worlds in terms of tone. On one hand, you have the natural, deep, and inherent timbre of the acoustic instrument itself, and on the other, a direct and almost electric bass flavor. This gives you an EZbass expansion with a sonic breadth that spans the entire range—from timeless acoustic resonance to sharp electric precision.\n\n\n\n\nIn addition to the instrument itself, the Acoustic EBX also includes a customizable MIDI library, as well as a set of presets covering ready-to-mix tones adapted for both amp and acoustic scenarios.\n\nIf you\'re a full-scale songwriter looking to enhance your EZbass with an instrument that can handle everything from backing up a single acoustic guitar and vocals to holding its own in a tight, full-band setup, this is your winning bet. Simply put: acoustic bass has never sounded so vibrant and stunningly good—until now.\n\nFEATURES\n- Meticulously captured acoustic bass\n- Ideal for use in singer-songwriter, acoustic, and folk songs\n- Recorded with both the built-in piezo pickup and an external condenser microphone\n- Includes a fingerstyle option, as well as a set of unique percussive articulations\n- Offering a range from D1 to E4\n- Includes a collection of presets covering a wide range of tones, from dark and earthy to bright, vibrant, and electric\n- Comes with a user MIDI library tailored to the instrument', 'https://torre9.com/images/ebxac.png', 'https://digistorage.net/nni4afqo', 'music', 'TOONTRACK', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 10:37:58', '2025-10-18 10:39:15', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(235, 'EBX Classic Rock para EZBass', '2023', '1.97 gb', 'win-mac', 'Libreria para EZBass de las mejores. EScucha su denso sonido', 'Publisher : Toontrack\nWebsite : Toontrack\nFormat : SOUNDBANK\nQuality : 24 bit 44.1 kHz stereo\n\nDescription : Classic Rock EBX is an expansion for EZbass featuring a meticulously recorded bass from the 1960s. This bass, selected for its optimal qualities, embodies all the desires and needs you\'d look for in a workhorse rock instrument: low frequencies, high harmonics, and that bright, distinct sustain that permeates any mix. Simply put, this is a bass that oozes rock with the strike of a single note.\n\nBeyond the instrument itself, EBX also includes a wide selection of presets and a customizable MIDI collection, making it much more than just a bass sample library—it\'s a treasure trove of ideas and a true toolbox.\n\nCan you imagine a killer groove without the raw power of bass? Without that deafening rumble that perfectly harmonizes with the drums and brings everything together into the thunderous wonder that is classic rock? Of course not. Meet the new classic rock bass!\n\nJohnBadger - Thank you so much!', 'https://torre9.com/images/ebxclr.png', 'https://digistorage.net/igg07r5p', 'music', 'TOONTRACK', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 10:43:16', '2025-10-18 10:57:07', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
