(244, 'AMPLITUBE 5.10 windows', '2025', '2.76 gb', 'windows', 'De los mejores procesadores de efectos virtuales para guitarra', '\nYear/Release Date : 10.2025\nVersion : v5.10.7\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s Website : **AmpliTube 5**\n\nFormat : SAL, VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : cured_TeamCubeadooby\nSystem requirements : Win 10+\nDescription : Legendary equipment on your Mac/PC Accurately reproduces the sound of more than 400 of the most popular models of equipment for bass and guitar.\n\nAmps, effects pedals, guitar cabinets, speakers, microphones, room effects, and rackmount effects - all in one interface with the routing you need.\n\n8-track recorder, DAW, looper, tuner - all the tools you need for work in one interface.\n\nAmpliTube 5 X provides full integration with TONEX to create your perfect rig in a single, elegant app. The free update introduces a new TONEX view, simplifying navigation of available tone models and offering filters by type, instrument, character, favorite, and skin to refine your search. Drag and drop tone models into your AmpliTube device chain or load them by skin from the right panel. Browse paid TONEX collections using advanced filters and use the new \"Open TONEX App\" button to quickly access the app to edit, rename, or download additional tone models from ToneNET.\n\nAdditional information :', 'https://torre9.com/images/amp.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/czdkpmt8', 'music', 'IK Multimedia ', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 11:32:30', '2026-01-04 14:36:31', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(245, 'TONEX MAX 1.10 windows', '2025', '2.87 gb', 'windows', 'Procesador de efectos para guitarra. Complementa muy bien con Amplitube 5', 'Year/Release Date : 10.2025\nVersion : v.1.10.4\nDeveloper : IK Multimedia\nDeveloper\'s website : TONEX MAX\n\nFormat : STANDALONE, VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : cured_TeamCubeadobby\nSystem requirements : Win 10+\nDescription : TONEX software is a revolution in computer modeling of guitar hardware and the core of the TONEX ecosystem. Innovative AI Machine Modeling™ technology allows you to model any amp, cabinet, combo amp, or pedal for the first time and turn them into a plugin with a sound indistinguishable from the real thing. You can immediately play through 1,250+ premium tone models available online, as well as search and download over 20,000 tone models available on ToneNET in TONEX. Add to all this even more premium sounds and signature collections from our tone partners!\n\nFrom the rarest, one-of-a-kind amps to modern rider setups, TONEX brings you all the gear in the world.', 'https://torre9.com/images/tm.png', 'https://digistorage.net/htchhams', 'music', 'IK Multimedia ', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 11:35:44', '2025-10-18 11:35:44', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(246, 'Melodyne Studio 5 (mac)', '2024', '95.9 mb', 'mac', 'El mejor editor de voces (post grabación)', 'Melodyne Studio 5.4.2 [MAC] [au, vst3, app]\n\npicRelease year : 2024\nVersion : 5.4.2\nDeveloper : Celemony\nPlatform : Intel & Silicon\nTablet : not required [Moria]\nSystem requirements : macOS 10.12+\n\nDescription : Melodyne 5 is a powerful audio editor used for fine-tuning vocals and musical instruments. The program allows you to adjust pitch, rhythm, note duration, and even intonation with incredible precision. Unique note recognition technology makes Melodyne an indispensable tool for professionals and enthusiasts, working with both monophonic and polyphonic audio recordings. Integration with popular DAWs provides flexibility and ease of editing.\n\nMelodyne supports ARA (Audio Random Access), a technology that provides deep integration with digital audio workstations (DAWs). Thanks to ARA, Melodyne allows you to work with audio files directly within the DAW, without having to constantly switch between programs. This significantly simplifies the editing process and allows for real-time changes, which is especially useful when working with multi-layered projects. ARA makes working with audio even more efficient and flexible, improving the overall performance and usability of Melodyne.', 'https://torre9.com/images/ms5.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/aolul31s', 'music', 'Celemony', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 11:39:24', '2025-10-18 11:39:24', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(247, 'Melodyne Studio 5 (windows)', '2024', '122.1 mb', 'windows', 'El mejor editor de voces (post grabación) para windows', '\nYear/Date of Release : 07.2024\nVersion : 5.4.1.004\nDeveloper : Celemony\nDeveloper website : Celemony\nFormat : SAL, VST3, AAX(MOD)\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : cured (R2R)\n\nSystem requirements :\nWindows 7 or higher\n\nDescription :\nMelodyne gives you unrivaled access to all the musical details of your recordings and samples, note by note.\nThis is made possible by meticulous analysis that deeply penetrates your recordings and samples, recognizing and understanding the musical relationships within them:\nindividual notes and their characteristics, scales, keys, and chords, timing, tempo, and tone color.\nAnd with Melodyne, you can edit all of this intuitively, whether it\'s vocals or any instrument, including polyphonic ones like piano and guitar.', 'https://torre9.com/images/ms5.jpg', 'https://digistorage.net/qt7kpocf', 'music', 'Celemony', '2025-10-18', 'torrent', '2025-10-18 11:41:57', '2025-10-18 11:41:57', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
