(258, 'kiloHearts Subscription 2.4.3 VST/VSTi, VST3/VSTi3, AAX x64 [10.2025] (R2R) MASTERING', '2025', '3.67 gb', 'windows', 'Excelente pack de mastering profesional para windows', 'Year/Date of Release : 10.2025\nVersion : 2.4.3\nDeveloper : kiloHearts\nDeveloper\'s website : kiloHearts\nFormat : VST, VST3, AAX\nBit depth : 64bit\nTablet : cured (R2R)\n\nSystem requirements :\nWindows 7 - 11\n\nDescription :\nLISTADO : Carve EQ\nDisperser\nFaturator\nkHs 3-Band EQ\nkHs Bitcrush\nkHs Channel Mixer\nkHs Chorus\nkHs Comb Filter.\nkHs Compressor\nkHs Convolver\nkHs Delay\nkHs Distortion\nkHs Dual Delay\nkHs Dynamics\nkHs Ensemble\nkHs Filter\nkHs Flanger\nkHs Formant Filter\nkHs Frequency Shifter.\nkHs Gain\nkHs Gate\nkHs Haas\nkHs Ladder Filter\nkHs Limiter\nkHs Nonlinear Filter\nkHs Phase Distortion\nkHs Phaser\nkHs Pitch Shifter\nkHs Resonator\nkHs Reverb\nkHs Reverser\nkHs Ring Mod\nkHs Shaper Table\nkHs Shaper\nkHs Stereo\nkHs Tape Stop\nkHs Trance Gate\nkHs Transient Shaper\nkHs Filter Table\nkHs Clipper\nkHs Compactor\nMultipass\nPhase Plant\nSlice EQ\nSnap Heap\n\n\n\nThe kiloHearts Subscription gives you instant access to all Kilohearts plugins and all official content banks.\nThe kiloHearts Subscription includes our groundbreaking modular synthesizer, Phase Plant, as well as our other highly customizable modular effect hosts,\nall our effect plugins, and several exclusive content banks from professional artists and sound designers!\nOver 40 plugins and a growing number of content banks. All effects work as \"Snapins\" in our modular hosts, as well as as standalone plugins that you can use individually in your DAW.', 'https://torre9.com/images/ks.png', 'https://digistorage.net/38ws9n6t', 'music', 'KILLOHEARTS', '2025-10-19', 'torrent', '2025-10-19 13:11:38', '2025-10-19 13:11:38', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
