(277, 'STEINBERG SPECTRALAYERS PRO 12 (torrent)', '2024', '4.47', 'windows', 'Excelente editor de audio', 'STEINBERG SPECTRALAYERS PARA WINDOWSYear/Release Date : 09.2025\nVersion : 12.0.20\nDeveloper : Steinberg\nDeveloper\'s Website : Steinberg\n\nBit depth : 64-bit\nInterface language : Multilingual (Russian is missing)\nTablet : present (R2R)\nSystem requirements :\nWindows 11/10 (21H2 or higher)\nA 64-bit Intel Core i5 (4th generation or later) or AMD Ryzen\nA DirectX 11 compatible graphics card (DirectX 12 recommended),\nand an OpenGL 3.3 capable graphics adapter is required for both\n8 GB of RAM\n1920x1080 display resolution minimum is recommended\n\nDescription :\nSteinberg presents an updated version of its software designed for spectral audio editing.\n\nINSTRUCCIONES:\nDelete the previous version (recommendation from R2R, so it\'s your discretion)\n\nNote:\nIf you already have the certificate (R2RCA.cer) and Silk Emulator v1.4.0 installed , skip steps 1-3\n\n1. _ Install the R2RCA.cer certificate\nWin+R > type certmgr.msc > Enter > Trusted Root Certification Authorities > Certificates > Right-click \"Certificates\" > All tasks > Import > point to the R2RCA.cer file\n\nYou can check whether the certificate has been installed using the R2RCERTEST.exe file.\n2. _ Install Setup Steinberg Silk Emulator v1.4.0.exe\n\n3. _ Reboot the OS\n\n\n4. _ Install Setup SpectraLayers 12 v12.0.0.421.exe\nIf you need ARA integration, don\'t forget to install VST3\n5. Where to place the modules read _ in R2R.txt _ in the Steinberg.SpectraLayers.12.Models-R2R folder\n\n', NULL, 'https://digistorage.net/0mue6o6l', 'music', 'Steinberg', '2025-10-28', 'torrent', '2025-10-28 10:51:16', '2025-10-29 11:38:44', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
